title: CC Sig
text: Croissant Club de Sig, known as CC Sig for short, is an Algerian <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> club located in <a href="Sig%2C%20Algeria">Sig, Algeria</a>, <a href="Algeria">Algeria</a>. The club was founded in 1926. They currently play in the <a href="Ligue%20Nationale%20du%20Football%20Amateur">Ligue Nationale du Football Amateur</a>.
